  "faqs": [
    {
      "question": "What's included with my sponsorship or foursome?",
      "answer": "All packages include lunch, beverages, golf cart, and a swag bag. Sponsorship tiers also include signage, social media promotion, and additional perks depending on level."
    },
    {
      "question": "Can I register a single golfer instead of a foursome?",
      "answer": "The tournament is organized by foursomes. If you'd like to play individually, contact us and we'll pair you with a group."
    },
    {
      "question": "Where does the money go?",
      "answer": "100% of proceeds fund dream room makeovers for children with special needs through <a href='https://sunshineonaranneyday.com'>Sunshine on a Ranney Day</a>. Zeffy charges zero platform fees."
    },
    {
      "question": "Can I donate without playing?",
      "answer": "Absolutely! You can <a href='/donate/'>donate directly</a> or shop <a href='https://www.sunnyandranney.com/shop/' target='_blank'>Sunny & Ranney</a> — profits go directly to funding room makeovers."
    },
    {
      "question": "What is the format of the tournament?",
      "answer": "The tournament is a scramble format — perfect for players of all skill levels. It's about having fun and supporting a great cause."
    },
    {
      "question": "Is there a dress code?",
      "answer": "Standard golf attire is required. Collared shirts, golf shorts or pants, and soft-spike golf shoes."
    }
  ],
